      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARCHIE MCIVOR (4) was out of the placings last time when seventh at this track (19.33) but scored three back at this track (19.70). Solid record here at the distance winning three races. The form out of last race has been strong. Can make amends. RING A HOUDINI (7) has a strong record this track and trip with eight wins and five placings from 18 starts. Missed the frame latest (26.25) when fourth over 460m at Geelong in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. IS HE LUCKY (2) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. Below best last time at Warrnambool (22.52) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fourth. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. OLIVER KELTON (6) placed two back in a Grade 4/5 at Warragul then backed that up with a third (19.26) over 350m at this track last time.",
